text: Khandi Alexander (born September 4, 1957) is an American dancer, choreographer, and movie and television actress. She played the character Catherine Duke on NewsRadio and the character Jackie Robbins on ER. She is best known for the character Alexx Woods, a coroner on the CBS drama CSI: Miami.
